pan>.<span class=\"name\">Cbv</span>.<span class=\"name\">CbvSimprocPhase</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"The phase at which a `cbv_simproc` fires during cbv normalization.\n\n- `pre` (`↓`): Fires on each subexpression *before* cbv reduction, so arguments are still\n  unreduced. Runs before cbv-specific pre-steps (projection reduction, unfolding, etc.).\n- `eval` (`cbv_eval`): Fires during the post phase, after ground evaluation but *before*\n  `handleApp` attempts equation lemmas, unfolding, and recursion reduction.\n  Arguments have already been reduced.\n- `post` (`↑`, default): Fires during the post phase, *after* `handleApp` has attempted\n  standard reduction. Arguments have already been reduced.\n","docLink":"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Cbv/CbvSimproc.html#Lean.Meta.Tactic.Cbv.CbvSimprocPhase","kind":"inductive","line":21,"name":"Lean.Meta.Tactic.Cbv.CbvSimprocPhase","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Lean/Meta/Tactic/Cbv/CbvSimproc.lean#L21-L34"}}],"imports":["Lean.Compiler.InitAttr","Lean.Meta.Sym.Pattern","Lean.Meta.Sym.Simp.App","Lean.Meta.Sym.Simp.DiscrTree","Lean.Meta.Sym.Simp.Result","Lean.Meta.Sym.Simp.SimpM","Lean.ScopedEnvExtension"],"instances":[{"className":"Inhabited","name":"Lean.Meta.Tactic.Cbv.instInhabitedCbvSimprocPhase","typeNames":["Lean.Meta.Tactic.Cbv.CbvSimprocPhase"]},{"className":"BEq","name":"Lean.Meta.Tactic.Cbv.instBEqCbvSimprocPhase","typeNames":["Lean.Meta.Tactic.Cbv.CbvSimprocPhase"]},{"className":"Hashable","name":"Lean.Meta.Tactic.Cbv.instHashableCbvSimprocPhase","typeNames":["Lean.Meta.Tactic.Cbv.CbvSimprocPhase"]},{"className":"Repr","name":"Lean.Meta.Tactic.Cbv.instReprCbvSimprocPhase","typeNames":["Lean.Meta.Tactic.Cbv.CbvSimprocPhase"]},{"className":"Lean.ToExpr","name":"Lean.Meta.Tactic.Cbv.instToExprCbvSimprocPhase","typeNames":["Lean.Meta.Tactic.Cbv.CbvSimprocPhase"]},{"className":"Inhabited","name":"Lean.Meta.Tactic.Cbv.instInhabitedCbvSimprocOLeanEntry","typeNames":["Lean.Meta.Tactic.Cbv.CbvSimprocOLeanEntry"]},{"className":"BEq","name":"Lean.Meta.Tactic.Cbv.instBEqCbvSimprocEntry","typeNames":["Lean.Meta.Tactic.Cbv.CbvSimprocEntry"]},{"className":"Std.ToFormat","name":"Lean.Meta.Tactic.Cbv.instToFormatCbvSimprocEntry","typeNames":["Lean.Meta.Tactic.Cbv.CbvSimprocEntry"]},{"className":"Inhabited","name":"Lean.Meta.Tactic.Cbv.instInhabitedCbvSimprocs","typeNames":["Lean.Meta.Tactic.Cbv.CbvSimprocs"]},{"className":"Inhabited","name":"Lean.Meta.Tactic.Cbv.instInhabitedBuiltinCbvSimprocs","typeNames":["Lean.Meta.Tactic.Cbv.BuiltinCbvSimprocs"]},{"className":"Inhabited","name":"Lean.Meta.Tactic.Cbv.instInhabitedCbvSimprocDecl","typeNames":["Lean.Meta.Tactic.Cbv.CbvSimprocDecl"]},{"className":"Inhabited","name":"Lean.Meta.Tactic.Cbv.instInhabitedCbvSimprocDeclExtState","typeNames":["Lean.Meta.Tactic.Cbv.CbvSimprocDeclExtState"]}],"name":"Lean.Meta.Tactic.Cbv.CbvSimproc"}